{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"AgentSight","page":{"layout":"document","title":"AgentSight 快速开始","description":"安装 AgentSight，记录一个 agent 进程，并在本地 UI 中查看 session。","descriptionIsExcerpt":false,"bodyHtml":"<p>这个指南展示如何记录一个本地 agent 进程，并打开内置 Web UI。</p>\n<h2 id=\"前置条件\">前置条件</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>支持 eBPF 的 Linux。推荐 kernel 5.x 或更新版本。</li>\n<li>加载 eBPF 程序需要 root 权限。</li>\n<li>一个目标进程，例如 <code>claude</code>、<code>node</code> 或 <code>python</code>。</li>\n<li>如果从源码构建：需要 Rust、Node.js、clang/LLVM 和 libelf 开发头文件。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"安装-release-二进制\">安装 release 二进制</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">wget</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/agentsight/releases/download/v0.1.1/agentsight</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">chmod</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> +x</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> agentsight</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"记录-agent\">记录 agent</h2>\n<p>选择 agent 实际使用的进程 command name。</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># Claude Code。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> claude</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># Gemini CLI 通常表现为 node 进程。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> node</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># Python-based agent 应用。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> python</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>如果 agent 使用的 Node.js 二进制静态打包了 OpenSSL，可以显式传入 binary path：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --binary-path</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /usr/bin/node</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> node</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"打开-ui\">打开 UI</h2>\n<p>record 启动后，打开：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span>http://127.0.0.1:8080</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>UI 会展示当前 session 的进程树、事件时间线、日志和资源指标。</p>\n<h2 id=\"先检查什么\">先检查什么</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>确认目标进程出现在进程树里。</li>\n<li>查看 agent 下面的子进程和命令执行。</li>\n<li>在 LLM 请求或工具调用附近检查 timeline event。</li>\n<li>调试 parser 行为时，用 log view 查看原始 event payload。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"停止记录\">停止记录</h2>\n<p>在运行 AgentSight 的终端按 <code>Ctrl-C</code>。如果异常中断后仍有 eBPF 程序残留，可以重新启动 AgentSight 做清理，或使用仓库里的 cleanup script 卸载 stale probe。</p>","headings":[{"id":"前置条件","text":"前置条件","depth":2},{"id":"安装-release-二进制","text":"安装 release 二进制","depth":2},{"id":"记录-agent","text":"记录 agent","depth":2},{"id":"打开-ui","text":"打开 UI","depth":2},{"id":"先检查什么","text":"先检查什么","depth":2},{"id":"停止记录","text":"停止记录","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/agentsight/quickstart.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","createdAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","authors":[{"name":"LinuxDev9002","email":"linuxdev8883@example.com"}]},"path":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/","alternates":{"en":"/agentsight/quickstart/","zh":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"AgentSight","description":"基于 eBPF 的 LLM 与 AI agent 零插桩可观测工具。","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},"previous":{"title":"AgentSight 运行说明","description":"AgentSight 的权限、隐私、支持环境和部署建议。","href":"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/"},"next":{"title":"AgentSight 故障排查","description":"事件缺失、TLS hook 失败和 UI 问题的常见处理方法。","href":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"AgentSight","items":[{"title":"总览","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},{"title":"快速开始","href":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/"},{"title":"架构","href":"/zh/agentsight/architecture/"},{"title":"可视化","href":"/zh/agentsight/visualization/"},{"title":"运行说明","href":"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/"},{"title":"故障排查","href":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/"}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}